creator: Infotjenester AS
descriptionHtml:
This application requires a paid subscription from Infotjenester AS.

Delivered by Infotjenester AS - the leading HR system vendor in Norway.

Simployer mobile handles:
Key data for all employees (self service)
Sick leave and self declarations
Following up on sick leave
Holiday planning
Leave and time off
Messaging
descriptionShort: Mobile HR system in the sky, supporting the Scandinavian Leadership Model.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Added application portal as startup page.

title: Simployer

descriptionHtml:
Inspire, manage and evolve your workforce with us.

The Simployer Group offers market leading insight & decision support, education, and HRM software solutions.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
In this update, we've added 3 minor features in the app:
* recently searched users that allows you to access recently searched persons quicker,
* link to AHA platform that allows you to add your ideas for our products,
* deeplinking. You won't notice it in the app, but don't be surprised if 3rd party app (eg. &frankly or your browser) opens the Simployer app for you 🙂

What's more, we've fixed few bugs that you found irritating.
Among the fixes, there is a fix for authentication.
